::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Zardus' eyes follow Feline as she walks back to her seat, looking at her 
shape. He calmly looks at her as she blows him a kiss. DevilDuer, on the 
other hand, was nearly shaking in his seat. Her hands running over his chest 
and up to his shoulder excited him, and he couln't get his mind off it.

Zardus glances at DevilDuer for a moment, motioning with his head for the 
other to leave. DevilDuer stands up, smiling at Feline and walking out of the 
room.

"I think you'll manage," Zardus says to Feline as the door closes behind 
DevilDuer, grinning, "From the expertice with which you've managed to 
brainwash Devil, you won't have too much trouble."

Zardus relaxes in his chair, looking at Feline. "As soon as Bloodystrike and 
Skulletron get here, I'll explain the mission. You'll be accompanying 
Skulletron."
